      "title": "Fertilizer distribution for Tea estates begin",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Tea Small Holdings Development Authority says that they have commenced the distribution of the urea and other fertilizers for tea cultivation.",
        "The Chairman of the Tea Small Holdings Development Authority Thushara Priyadarshana said that fertilizers are distributed through small tea plantation societies and tea factories.",
        "The Chairman said that if there is a problem in obtaining fertilizer, to contact the hotline 1974.",
        "Weak Regulators Framework root cause for loan issue \u2013 Verite\u2019"
      ],
